TO RUN THE PROJECT:

1) Run the codes
cd SDBroker
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
sudo yay -S pyzmq               (or just use whatever downloader you have installed to download the pyzmq package)

2) In different terminals run, in this order:
python env.py
python sensor_thread.py
python manager.py

3) And then, in another terminal, pass the room you want to monitor as a parameter. The rooms go up to 8 with the pattern "RN1", "RN2", etc.
python client.py username [id_room]
